casebody.data:
September 17, 1958. No. 87,

October Term, 1958.

Allen N. Spooner & Sons, Inc., et al. v. Port of New York Authority. Martin J. McHugh was on the stipulation for petitioners. With him on the petition was Thomas F. Daly. John M. Aherne was on the stipulation for respondent.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit. Dismissed per stipulation pursuant to Rule 60 of the Rules of this Court.
